вЂЄDo you know the devil. Mom? Hmm?

396
00:18:37.916 --> 00:18:40.666
вЂЄYou haven't seen the devil yet. Mom. Okay?

397
00:18:40.750 --> 00:18:41.958
вЂЄNow get the hell out of my way.

398
