вЂЄ-You're not going anywhere. Hey!
вЂЄ-I said move!

399
00:18:44.416 --> 00:18:45.708
вЂЄ-Mom!
вЂЄ-You're not going anywhere.

400
00:18:45.791 --> 00:18:47.250
вЂЄ-Mom! Mom!
вЂЄ-You're notвЂ¦ [screams]

401
00:18:47.333 --> 00:18:48.958
вЂЄ-[screaming]
вЂЄ-[grunts]

402
00:18:49.666 --> 00:18:51.166
вЂЄMom! Mom!

403
00:18:51.750 --> 00:18:53.958
